[09:35.75] And live the purer with the other half.
[09:39.23] Good night: but go not to mine uncle's bed;
[09:44.57] Assume a virtue, if you have it not.
[09:47.12] That monster, custom, who all sense doth eat,
[09:49.54] Of habits devil, is angel yet in this,
