[10:16.31] I'll blessing beg of you. For this same lord,
[10:20.84] [Pointing to POLONIUS]
[10:21.71] I do repent: but heaven hath pleased it so,
[10:23.83] To punish me with this and this with me,
[10:25.87] That I must be their scourge and minister.
[10:29.16] I will bestow him, and will answer well
